OL,3,C'Severe disruption' expected as 600
OL,4,Cbus drivers walk out over pay
OL,6,F"Severe disruption" is expected in
OL,7,Fcentral Bristol as some bus drivers go
OL,8,Fon strike next week, the Unite union
OL,9,Fsays.
OL,11,FThe industrial action by 600 bus
OL,12,Fdrivers on First West of England's
OL,13,FCity Line services will take place
OL,14,Ffrom next Tuesday 16 September to
OL,15,FFriday 19 September.
OL,17,FThe drivers, who are members of Unite,
OL,18,Foperate out of the Lawrence Hill and
OL,19,FHengrove Bus depots.
