OL,6,FThese depots serve inner-city bus
OL,7,Froutes in the city as well as Bristol
OL,8,FAirport, the local universities and
OL,9,FAmazon's Bristol warehouse.
OL,11,FThe union says that due to the number
OL,12,Fof drivers involved, the industrial
OL,13,Faction will cause a lot of
OL,14,Fcancellations and delays to services.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for First Bus said a
OL,17,Frevised timetable had been drawn up to
OL,18,Freflect the strikes.
