OL,6,FPrevious industrial action from 4 to 8
OL,7,FSeptember had been suspended to allow
OL,8,FUnite members to be balloted on a new
OL,9,Fpay offer, after drivers previously
OL,10,Frejected a two-year pay deal.
OL,12,FHowever, members have now voted to
OL,13,Freject the latest offer from First
OL,14,FWest of England.
OL,16,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,17,Fsaid: "First Group is a very
OL,18,Fprofitable company and can afford to
OL,19,Fcome back with an improved offer that
OL,20,Fis acceptable to our bus drivers.
