OL,6,F"Unite will fully support our members
OL,7,Fthroughout their strike action, which
OL,8,Fhas been caused by the employer
OL,9,Fputting profits over people."
OL,11,FUnite regional officer, Ken Fish,
OL,12,Fsaid: "There is still an opportunity
OL,13,Ffor First West of England to come back
OL,14,Fto the negotiating table to stop this
OL,15,Fdisruptive strike action."
