OL,6,FPlanned strikes on the same dates next
OL,7,Fweek by 400 drivers at First West of
OL,8,FEngland's Badgerline working at the
OL,9,FBristol Marlborough Street, Bath,
OL,10,FWells and Weston-super-Mare depots
OL,11,Fhave been called off after members
OL,12,Fvoted to accept an improved pay offer
OL,13,Ffrom the company.
