OL,6,F"We have put together revised
OL,7,Ftimetables to reflect the much lower
OL,8,Flevel of service that we will be able
OL,9,Fto operate on these days.
OL,11,F"Details of these will shortly be
OL,12,Favailable on our website and we advise
OL,13,Fcustomers to check for updates before
OL,14,Ftravelling.
OL,16,F"While this was our full and final pay
OL,17,Foffer, we still hope to find a
OL,18,Fsolution with the trade union which
OL,19,Fencourages them to call off these
OL,20,Fdisruptive strikes."
